  title: "Creating a team of agile pioneers"
  content: "Embedding our team into the Reed Learning team allowed us to introduce agile and lean ways of working in this traditionally waterfall organisation. Before beginning this transformation, we had to ensure we were in a position to start delivering from day one. With ceremonies, systems and our working space all set up, in place and ticked off our checklist, the newly formed Reed Learning / Unboxed team was in a strong position to begin delivering results."
