  source: "Melissa Sabella, Director of Product and Innovation, Reed Learning"

piloting:
  title: "Piloting the team’s first agile project"
  content: "Starting small, as a first step, the team launched a pilot agile project. This pilot wasn’t so big that it could be a major risk, but was large enough to make an impact and create positive waves across the organisation. Fortnightly Show & Tells were scheduled involving stakeholders in this new way of working. These sessions were used to provide regular updates on the most important delivered work and priorities, building up trust between stakeholders and the team."
  image: "/project-stories/reed-learning/office.jpg"
  image_description: "A Meeting, but Agile"

quote_3:
